text: Jennifer Luff (born 7 January 1966) is an Australian rower. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sydney
